content:
The AI Conference 2025 FAQ - General Information

The AI Conference 2025 is an in-person event located at Pier 48, Mission Rock, San Francisco, CA 94158. It takes place on September 17th-18th, 2025, starting at 8:00 AM PST.  The conference focuses on AGI, LLMs, Infrastructure, Alignment, AI Startups, and Neural Architectures. Contact info@aiconference.com for questions.
overview: General event details including location, date, and contact information.

content:
The AI Conference 2025 - Sponsorship & Parking

Companies interested in sponsoring the conference can find information at aiconference.com/sponsors/. Parking information is available at ParkWiz: https://www.parkwhiz.com/pier-48-parking/?daily=1
overview: Information regarding sponsorship opportunities and parking options.

content:
The AI Conference 2025 - Cost & Discounts

The conference offers Early Bird pricing. Standard pass prices are available on the registration page. Group rates are available for groups of three or more; contact tickets@aiconference.com for a discount code.
overview: Details about conference costs, discounts, and group rates.

content:
The AI Conference 2025 - Cancellation & Code of Conduct

Refunds are available up to 30 days prior to the event, with a 5% fee.  The conference code of conduct can be found at aiconference.com/code-of-conduct/
overview: Information on the cancellation policy and the conference's code of conduct.

content:
The AI Conference 2025 - Registration & Presentations

Attendees with press, vendor, or speaker passes will receive emails with event details. Speaker submissions will open soon; sign up for the speakers interest list at aiconference.com/cfp/. Press passes can be applied for shortly. Presentations will be 40 minutes (Keynote) or 20 minutes (featured contributors).
overview: Details for attendees with specific pass types, speaker submissions, and presentation formats.

content:
The AI Conference 2025 - Presentation Topics & Areas

The conference will cover topics including AGI development, Foundation Models, Generative AI, Neural Architectures, AI Infrastructure, Ethics, AI Startups, and Data Management. There are 4 presentation halls, a vendor/sponsor area, and networking areas.
overview: Overview of the topics covered and the presentation areas available at the conference.

content:
The AI Conference 2025 - Nearby Hotels

Several hotels are near the event venue: Luma Hotel San Francisco (0.3 miles, booking cutoff 8/29/2025), Hotel VIA (0.6 miles, cutoff 8/18/2025), SoMa House (1.9 miles, cutoff 7/16/2025), and Hotel Fiona (1.9 miles, cutoff 7/16/2025). Booking links are provided.
overview: Information about nearby hotels with booking links and cutoff dates.
